definition: one/1/single/a (article)/as soon as/entire/whole/all/throughout/"one" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 1)/also pr. [yao1] for greater clarity when spelling out numbers digit by digit

sentences.english: Since november ordinarily of it early stoped action.
sentences.chinese: 既然是十一月，他们早就该停止活动了。

sentences.english: It is November, but it is very hot.
sentences.chinese: 现在是十一月，但是天气很热。

sentences.english: Judging by the signs, could be late November, early December.
sentences.chinese: 从现象来看，可能是十一月底，十二月初了吧。

sentences.english: He conked out in November with pleurisy.
sentences.chinese: 他患肋膜炎于十一月份死去。

sentences.english: It was the end of November and the day was very cheerless.
sentences.chinese: 已经是十一月底了，天色十分阴暗。

sentences.english: Mayday's first performance in November came off very well.
sentences.chinese: 五月天十一月份的首场演出非常成功。

sentences.english: Today is November first! nineteen sixty-three.
sentences.chinese: 这日是一九六三年十一月一号。

sentences.english: The team will return to India to continue studying Koro in November.
sentences.chinese: 这支探险队会在十一月份回到印度继续研究珂珞语。

sentences.english: The weather gets cold in November, and nothing is better than staying at your familiar hotel, working hard.
sentences.chinese: 在这初冬寒风起的十一月，还是躲进小楼成一统。

sentences.english: Mine is Topaz which is the birthstone of November.
sentences.chinese: 我出生于十一月，所以我的生辰石是托帕石。

sentences.english: Trading in Gome’s shares on Hong Kong’s stock exchange was suspended on November 24th.
sentences.chinese: 在港上市的国美股票于十一月二十四日停盘。

sentences.english: We shall achieve your order by November 30.
sentences.chinese: 我们会在十一月卅日前完成您的订单需逑。

sentences.english: I was born on November first, nineteen ninety-five.
sentences.chinese: 我是一九九五年十一月一日出生的。

sentences.english: Flaked with patches of snow, as hedges sometimes in November.
sentences.chinese: 落上了斑斑雪霜，像十一月里的树篱矮桩。

sentences.english: November is for thanksgiving, count God's bounteous graces.
sentences.chinese: 十一月是感恩的季节，细数神所赐的丰盛恩典。

sentences.english: Huating County to resume in November 1961.
sentences.chinese: 一九六一年十一月恢复华亭县。
